item.title: Conservative Private Member's Bill corrections
item.description: Conservatives introduce law to indirectly “defend” the fetus The Conservative Party of Canada announced, on their website, the addition of a Private Member’s Bill by MP Cathay Wagantall. The Bill has numerous statistical errors and also appears to be yet another attempt by a Conservative Party MP to push anti-abortion legislation under the guise of trying to stand up to crime.
